{"tid":2007450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【理大衝突】被控暴動罪 2位手足不准保釋","createTime":"2020-05-08T10:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T10:36:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa59f0873384a66bbe096ebcee69562a9e31da74","tid":2007450,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"法庭文字直播台 <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F4900&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=6b7f2843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4900</a> <br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#嚴舜儀署理主任裁判官 <br />\n#新案件 <br />\n<br />\nD1施<br />\nD2文<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1. 管有攻擊性武器<br />\n2. 管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n3. 暴動<br />\n<br />\n案情：被指於11月18日加士居道天橋管有2把刀及1把槌，利用水馬向警方防線推進，在車路棄置疑似電油。在九龍油麻地加士居道天橋近伊利沙白醫院，與其他不知名人士參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">‼️保釋申請被拒‼️還押懲教看管🚐</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n於5月15日保釋覆核<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至7月17日九龍城裁判法院第一庭再訊"},{"pid":"e5a56b10d7f5b69b2b31aaf797fb952c8378852e","tid":2007450,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d328f881c6248290936164a1f9a8964184aeb49","tid":2007450,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:34:06.000Z","msg":"屌曬你班散水撚，同我即刻番poly，poly根本係城堡/要塞黎。邊個話守唔到？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f224e92eadd02f720703fbe7049f583f74ef40d","tid":2007450,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又屈"},{"pid":"3aee0808f58435a3496e29169137992d2313fa28","tid":2007450,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB